    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem, and let me tell you\u2014it\u2019s a total stunner. It\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is in truly pristine, like-new condition inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person! If you\u2019re looking for a car that\u2019s been pampered its whole life, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 46500.0,
