    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive example of the 996.2 generation. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, this unit delivers a sharp, linear throttle response through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The wide-body chassis retains factory-spec lateral rigidity, supported by an advanced AWD system and 'Big Red' four-piston monobloc calipers. This vehicle is mechanically flawless, with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a completely dry crankcase. The exterior finish and interior appointments are in showroom state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous preventative maintenance.",
